data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Don't miss your opportunity to tour this gem waiting for it's next owners to come in and customize to their desires. For under $200k, you can purchase a home within walking distance to the stadiums, public transportation, local parks, restaurants and major highways. The kitchen remodel was started and is waiting for the new owner to come add those finishing touches. Don't forget to check out the decent side yard where you will want to entertain on those summer nights! This 3 bedroom, one bathroom, unfinished basement is waiting for YOU!
